caption: Paris is piled, stuffed and encrusted with ancient, beautiful and precious artifacts but this believer’s heart sprang up with recognition  when I wandered into this humble sanctuary and found myself among family.  An old song comes to mind:  “There’s a sweet sweet spirit in this place; and I know that it’s the spirit of the Lord. There’s a sweet expression on each face and I know that it’s the spirit of the Lord”.  I’m grateful to this little congregation for lifting up Jesus Christ who unites us all, wherever we wandered in from.
English Service. Very friendly people from diverse backgrounds, preaching from the bible.
